{"id":2295,"date":"2015-10-28T03:38:38","date_gmt":"2015-10-28T10:38:38","slug":"we-are-blood-brasil","title":"PRO BONO PROMO: We Are Blood &#8211; Brasil","content":"<p><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/krak/id916474561\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-2297\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/Screen-Shot-2015-10-28-at-3.08.09-AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2015-10-28 at 3.08.09 AM\" width=\"300\" height=\"188\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/Screen-Shot-2015-10-28-at-3.08.09-AM.png 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1024/mag/uploads/Screen-Shot-2015-10-28-at-3.08.09-AM.png 1024w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1080/mag/uploads/Screen-Shot-2015-10-28-at-3.08.09-AM.png 1080w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/Screen-Shot-2015-10-28-at-3.08.09-AM.png 1440w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/krak/id916474561\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-2298\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/Screen-Shot-2015-10-28-at-3.08.12-AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2015-10-28 at 3.08.12 AM\" width=\"300\" height=\"188\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/Screen-Shot-2015-10-28-at-3.08.12-AM.png 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1024/mag/uploads/Screen-Shot-2015-10-28-at-3.08.12-AM.png 1024w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1080/mag/uploads/Screen-Shot-2015-10-28-at-3.08.12-AM.png 1080w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/Screen-Shot-2015-10-28-at-3.08.12-AM.png 1440w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></p>\n<p>For this week&#8217;s PRO BONO PROMO, we feature Brain Farm Skate&#8217;s <a href=\"https://streamingmoviesright.com/us/movie/we-are-blood/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">We Are Blood</a> &#8211; Brasil promo. While the video has been out for a good minute, just in case you haven&#8217;t caught it yet, here&#8217;s the Brasil promo to whet your appetite.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/krak/id916474561\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-2300\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/Screen-Shot-2015-10-28-at-3.08.56-AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2015-10-28 at 3.08.56 AM\" width=\"300\" height=\"188\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/Screen-Shot-2015-10-28-at-3.08.56-AM.png 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1024/mag/uploads/Screen-Shot-2015-10-28-at-3.08.56-AM.png 1024w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1080/mag/uploads/Screen-Shot-2015-10-28-at-3.08.56-AM.png 1080w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/Screen-Shot-2015-10-28-at-3.08.56-AM.png 1440w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a><a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/krak/id916474561\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-2303\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/Screen-Shot-2015-10-28-at-3.09.02-AM.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2015-10-28 at 3.09.02 AM\" width=\"300\" height=\"188\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_300/mag/uploads/Screen-Shot-2015-10-28-at-3.09.02-AM.png 300w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1024/mag/uploads/Screen-Shot-2015-10-28-at-3.09.02-AM.png 1024w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/w_1080/mag/uploads/Screen-Shot-2015-10-28-at-3.09.02-AM.png 1080w, https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/Screen-Shot-2015-10-28-at-3.09.02-AM.png 1440w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Featuring a little narrative (in Portuguese and English) of the scene in Brazil, specifically Sao Paulo and Rio de Janeiro, as well as snippets of phenomenal skating from Tiago Lemos, Rodrigo Petersen, Alex Carolino, Danny Cerizini, Marcelo Formiga, Kaue Cossa, Vinicius Santos and many many more. Definitely conveys the energy of the Brazilian scene. And yes, you even get to peep two angles of Tiago&#8217;s ridiculous front pop shove! Check it out below. -HK</p>\n<p><iframe title=\"We Are Blood - Brasil\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/XVjrK-oOqHs?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n","author":"kev","categories":["reviews"],"tags":["alex-carolino","brasil","brazil","danny-cerizini","kaue-cossa","marcelo-formiga","rodrigo-petersen","tiago-lemos","vinicius-santos","we-are-blood"],"featuredImages":[{"file":"Screen-Shot-2015-10-28-at-3.51.39-AM.png","width":1440,"height":900,"mime_type":"image/png","source_url":"https://res.cloudinary.com/krak/image/upload/mag/uploads/Screen-Shot-2015-10-28-at-3.51.39-AM.png"}],"video":""}